HEADWORD: Crotalaria
<hw>Crot`a*la"ri*a</hw> <pr>(kr?t`?-l?"r?-? ⟦or⟧
kr?`t?-l?"r?-A)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Crotalum</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of leguminous
plants; rattlebox.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ <spn>Crotalaria juncea</spn> furnishes the fiber called
<xex>sunn</xex> or <xex>Bombay hemp</xex>.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

